{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_13_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よいしょ……\n紙も量が多いと結構重いな……",
      "startTime": 3.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2045806408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、いらっしゃい\n大きな袋を抱えて、どうしたの？",
      "startTime": 9.2379139741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 266.66666669999995,
          "startTime": 7.4712473075
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "事務所に届いていたファンレターを持って来たんです\n……って、なんですか、その格好は！　ハレンチな！",
      "startTime": 15.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9780272961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "誰がハレンチよ！　これはクリスマスイベントで\n着る衣装よ。変なこと言わないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 22.6646939437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今日はたまたま試着していただけで\n普段からこんな格好してる訳じゃないから",
      "startTime": 29.4646939437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2813604197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。でも俺の記憶だと、衣装のデザインは\nこんなに露出が多くなかったはずですが……",
      "startTime": 36.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ララ達のイベント出演が決まって\n彼女達の衣装も追加で作ることになったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 43.0485488098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8052141669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "でも急な話で材料は増やせないから、限られた材料で\n追加分の衣装も作れるようにアレンジしたの",
      "startTime": 51.4818808716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "その結果、元のデザインよりも\n一人分の布面積がかなり少なくなったのよ",
      "startTime": 57.3152142049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8121304991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスにこの露出はかなり寒そうですが\n莉央さんは大丈夫なんですか？",
      "startTime": 64.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.5038536233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "私が何年アイドルをやってると思ってるの？\n冬でも薄着で仕事することなんてめずらしくもないわ",
      "startTime": 70.4736039957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい大したことないわよ\nそれより、私のこの姿を見て他に言うことはないの？",
      "startTime": 76.8069373291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.2238534134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、はい、凄く似合ってます。美人でスタイル抜群の\n莉央さんにぴったりで、思わず見とれてしまいそうです",
      "startTime": 86.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.6832410654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう……私に見とれて……\nちょっと、そんなにじろじろ見ないで",
      "startTime": 95.2329916478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ？　さっきまで堂々としていたのに）\n（急に顔が赤くなったぞ？）",
      "startTime": 101.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 104.6365737438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、やけに部屋が散らかっていますね\n見たことのない機械が沢山転がっていますが……",
      "startTime": 110.0333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "それは全部ララの私物よ\n彼女はここで発明品を作ったり改造したりしているの",
      "startTime": 116.4470747154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "私が着ているこの衣装も\nここでララが改造したものなのよ",
      "startTime": 122.8137403648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、あそこの機械が、ララ達がこの世界に来た原因と\nなった『ぴょんぴょんワープくんDXカスタム』よ",
      "startTime": 129.5470736981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達が元の世界に帰るには、エネルギーを集めて\nあの機械を動かしてワープしないといけないの",
      "startTime": 137.4470736981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、アイドルのライブで発生する膨大な想いの\nエネルギーを集められるように衣装を改造したのよ",
      "startTime": 144.4137403648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "見た目はただの衣装にしか見えませんが、その中には\n宇宙人の高度な技術が詰まっているんですね",
      "startTime": 152.0852798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "他にも沢山機械が転がっていますが\nこれも全部、ララさんの発明品なんですか？",
      "startTime": 158.6666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ。こころが面白がってララに頼んで\nいろんな発明品を見せてもらっていたの",
      "startTime": 165.4618121624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "こころったら「この発明品はいたずらに使えそうです」\nって、悪い顔をしながら説明を聞いていたわ",
      "startTime": 172.3951454957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うかつに触っちゃダメよ\nこの間も勝手に触って大変なことになったんだから",
      "startTime": 178.2618121624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "そこにある掃除機とか、そっちの荷造り用のロープとか\nあそこのマッサージ機とか……",
      "startTime": 186.0951454957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "どれも最終的にみんなの服がはだけて\n大騒ぎになったのよ",
      "startTime": 192.0284788291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なぜその機械で服が脱げるのか\n意味が分からないんですが",
      "startTime": 196.6333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "私にも分からないわよ\n発明品を作ったララに悪気はないんでしょうけど……",
      "startTime": 200.6115627606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "あれはもう、えっちなアクシデントが起こる呪いが\nかかっているとしか思えないわ",
      "startTime": 207.8782294273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "あんな発明品を作ってるくせに\nララは天真爛漫ないい子なのよね……",
      "startTime": 213.0115464846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
